desc: Featuring exclusive merch from the YouTube channel Blind Wave.

layout.text:
The Original Blind Wave Logo is officially retired and has been locked away in our vault at the Wave Cave.
While we're sad to see it go, we're also HYPED to finally release our brand new 2021 Blind Wave Logo merch collection!
You might have spotted us 'leaking' a few items here and there in various videos and streams... (we couldn't help it) ...and we're excited for you to check it out!
